    How to find the best technology images?
    When you're looking for the best technology images, it's important to remember that you can't just save an image you find on the internet and use it in your projects. Many images are protected by copyright, so you need permission. Shutterstock's library of stock and royalty-free images is fully licensed, meaning you can get the rights you need to use the images however you want. Simply head over to shutterstock.com, and type your search keyword into the search field. When you get your results, you can use the filters on the left-hand side of the page to narrow down your options. With options like orientation, image type, color scheme, and even with or without people, you can fully customize your search and find precisely the image you're looking for.
    How to download free technology images?
    Downloading free images is easy, but before you head out to the internet and start downloading everything you see, remember that images are subject to copyright, so you need permission to use them in your projects. The stock and royalty-free images in the Shutterstock library are ready to license, so you don't need to worry about permissions. To try the Shutterstock image collection, simply head to the free technology image collection on this page, and download it with one click. This free sample collection is yours to use.
